<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Advanced Program Website</title>
<style>
  /* Reset and base styles */
  *, *::before, *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background: #f0f4f8; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  a {
    color: #0078a0; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  a:hover, a:focus {
    color: #00475a; outline: none;
  }
  header {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #005980, #0099cc);
    color: white; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  header nav {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0;
  }
  nav ul {
    list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  }
  nav ul li a {
    font-weight: 600; padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
  }
  nav ul li a:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid #80b3c9; outline-offset: 3px;
  }

  main {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr)); gap: 2rem;
  }
  section.card {
    background: white; padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  section.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  section.card h2 {
    margin-top: 0; color: #005980; font-size: 1.6rem;
  }
  section.card p {
    flex-grow: 1; margin: 1em 0;
  }
  section.card ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem; margin: 0.5em 0 1em 0;
  }
  section.card ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  button {
    background: #0078a0; color: white; border: none; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  button:hover, button:focus {
    background: #00475a; outline: none;
  }

  /* Responsive hero section */
  .hero {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80') no-repeat center/cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    height: 300px;
    color: white; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* Footer styles */
  footer {
    text-align: center; padding: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; background: #eaeaea;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  /* Form Styles */
  form {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
  }
  label {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  input, textarea, select {
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 6px; width: 100%;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus {
    border-color: #0078a0; outline: none;
  }
  textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 100px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header role="banner">
  <nav role="navigation" aria-label="Primary navigation">
    <h1>Advanced Program</h1>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#about" tabindex="0">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#features" tabindex="0">Features</a></li>
      <li><a href="#enroll" tabindex="0">Enroll</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact" tabindex="0">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="hero" role="region" aria-label="Welcome section">
    <h1>Empowering Your Future with Advanced Technology</h1>
    <p>Join our cutting-edge program to master the skills that define tomorrow.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="card" role="region" aria-labelledby="about-title">
    <h2 id="about-title">About The Program</h2>
    <p>This advanced program covers modern web development, AI, machine learning, and software engineering best practices. Designed for ambitious learners looking to excel in technology careers.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="features" class="card" role="region" aria-labelledby="features-title">
    <h2 id="features-title">Program Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Comprehensive curriculum including HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and AI fundamentals</li>
      <li>Hands-on projects and live coding sessions</li>
      <li>Expert instructors with industry experience</li>
      <li>Flexible online learning with resource-rich content</li>
      <li>Industry-recognized certification upon completion</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="enroll" class="card" role="region" aria-labelledby="enroll-title">
    <h2 id="enroll-title">Enroll Now</h2>
    <form aria-label="Enrollment form">
      <label for="name">Full Name *</label>
      <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required aria-required="true" placeholder="Your full name" />

      <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
      <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required aria-required="true" placeholder="Your email" />

      <label for="program">Select Program *</label>
      <select id="program" name="program" required aria-required="true">
        <option value="" disabled selected>Choose a program</option>
        <option value="web-development">Web Development</option>
        <option value="ai-and-ml">AI & Machine Learning</option>
        <option value="software-engineering">Software Engineering</option>
      </select>

      <label for="message">Additional Information</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Any questions or requests"></textarea>

      <button type="submit">Submit Enrollment</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="card" role="region" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
    <h2 id="contact-title">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Have any questions? Reach out to us!</p>
    <address>
      Email: <a href="mailto:info@advancedprogram.com">info@advancedprogram.com</a><br />
      Phone: <a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 234 567 890</a><br />
      Address: 123 Tech Avenue, Innovation City, Country
    </address>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  &copy; 2025 Advanced Program. All rights reserved.
</footer>

<script>
  // Basic client-side form validation example
  document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    if(!this.checkValidity()) {
      alert('Please fill all required fields correctly before submitting.');
      e.preventDefault();
    }
  });
</script>
</body>
</html